songs.title: DAUGHTER*
songs.lyrics:
[Verse]
...
Pump make a nigga drop out like Harvard
Pocket full of green, but the shit ain't collard
Lost my marbles, no mancala
Untame when I'm in a Tame Impala
Impalas pull up on baller
Big baller, call the nigga Saitama
My llama sing like Alana
Shock a nigga, you can call me Rayden
When I switch the cadence, bitch, I'm too amazing
Call a nigga Ronald Wilson Reagan
That's from triple 6's, 'cause my shit is blazing
Snatch a nigga daughter like it's Taken
If a nigga try me, then you know he hatin'
Super Samus, where the Superman
Come down to hoes, I'm never savin'

[Chorus]
Wanna see a star? Go to Macy's
Brand new phones, never raid these
Bullets to your home like Katie's
Slaughter your daughter like Casey
Wanna see a star? Go to Macy's
Brand new phones, never raid these
Bullets to your home like Katie's
